        // "it is not part of some longer word satisfying the condition." 
        // By extracting maximal contiguous segments of [a-z-], we satisfy the maximality part.

        // We need to verify the hyphen rule: every hyphen must be between two letters.
        // Pattern: [a-z]+(?:-[a-z]+)*
